<head>FERTILISE</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">使肥沃</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>AGRICULTURAL WORK INTENDING to CAUSE TO BECOME FERTILE.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The standard word for fertilising fields with manure is fèn 糞.</p>
        </div>
